parameters: There's a door, it is unlocked but there are sounds coming from within.
Door is locked, it looks like it hasn't been used in ages.
Perhaps there's a key for it in another room.
A long abandoned minecart, the wheels fail to turn due to rust.
This large gate is locked but it needs a special key to unlock. Perhaps it's somewhere in here.
With a loud bang, the lock released.
There's a hole with pure energy flowing forth. If you reach in, you may gain untold amounts of power.
Strength to destroy any enemy in your path and save your friends.
Do you want to reach in and accept this power?
You can't believe your eyes. It's real. Your veins glow as it travels through you.
With a breath of fresh air..... you....
The badly damaged door is locked. You'll need a key for this.
I have a bad feeling about this, \N[1].
Yeah.... me too. It'll be okay though. We've got this.
How are you always so sure about these things?
We're strong people and no matter what we face, we'll get through it. You just have to believe.
